code: public <T> T newInstance(Class<T> type) {     Object value = applicationContext.getBeanFactory().createBean(type, autowireMode, dependencyCheck).     return type.cast(value). }
public void setAutowireMode(int autowireMode) {     this.autowireMode = autowireMode. }
public void setDependencyCheck(boolean dependencyCheck) {     this.dependencyCheck = dependencyCheck. }
